{"tid":617552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度老虎闖民宅　少女持棍決鬥險死","createTime":"2018-04-05T05:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T05:16:30.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3f5f18f7714b1e9986af3ee7b5f9c3dc21d16e5","tid":617552,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"中國小說有「武松打虎」，現實中，印度西部馬哈拉施特拉邦有位「女版武松」，持棍棒與襲擊羊群的老虎一戰。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n23歲的梅什蘭姆（Rupali Meshram）上周聽到山羊慘叫聲後走出屋外察看，發現有老虎闖入。她拿了一根棍棒擊向老虎，老虎還擊。她的媽媽吉賈巴伊（Jijabhai）見到女兒與老虎相鬥，趕忙出來將女兒拉回屋內。山羊最終性命不保，老虎在森林警衛到場前跑了。母女皆被老虎所傷，經治療後已經出院。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n梅什蘭姆的頭、腰、手腳都受到皮外傷，事後還自拍血流滿面照。醫師讚她勇氣可嘉，認為她沒有被虎咬是相當幸運。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n吉賈巴伊事後表示，見女兒奮力嘗試趕走老虎，導致全身受傷流血，還以為她必死無疑。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"9b2ccfe870299c2d40ecf818ec8063b639b3210a","tid":617552,"uid":133776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"樓主老母趕老虎險死"},{"pid":"f509afa8a15b9ff1d391dfada28d6e111c021425","tid":617552,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:09:59.000Z","msg":"如果有槍就無事啦"},{"pid":"e12cf3b916906eef66791c50bc9b877280c9bc9f","tid":617552,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"落後地區的人民特別勇武"},{"pid":"00ce24a899053186cf4ca657b40ae85d457943bb","tid":617552,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"香港賤民趕馬嬲都俾動物撚話虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86aa51dfb522b8ea11432762deec6237bb826121","tid":617552,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"老虎還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老虎心諗佢真係夠膽郁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}